{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/data-science/levenshtein-distance/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"renuevo blog","author":"deokhwa kim","siteUrl":"https://renuevo.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"https-renuevo-github-io","utterances":""},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":""}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"d81a6f68-2cdb-53f4-9b00-38364129b8d1","excerpt":"Levenshtein Distance (편집거리 알고리즘) 는 러시아의 과학자 블라디미르 리벤슈테인가 고안한 알고리즘   Levenshtein Distance이 무엇일까? 오늘날 언어학/데이터과학 같이 폭 넓게 사용되고 있으며 문장과 DNA 유사도 분석같은 곳에 사용되고 있습니다 레벤슈타인 알고리즘의 비교 이론은 간단합니다      이렇게 두 개의 비교군을 분석하여 연산되는 비용이 높을 수록 서로 다른겁니다   Levenshtein Distance…","html":"<h1 id=\"levenshtein-distance-편집거리-알고리즘\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#levenshtein-distance-%ED%8E%B8%EC%A7%91%EA%B1%B0%EB%A6%AC-%EC%95%8C%EA%B3%A0%EB%A6%AC%EC%A6%98\" aria-label=\"levenshtein distance 편집거리 알고리즘 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Levenshtein Distance (편집거리 알고리즘)</h1>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Levenshtein Distance</code>는 러시아의 과학자 <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vladimir_Levenshtein\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">블라디미르 리벤슈테인</a>가 고안한 알고리즘  </p>\n<br/>\n<h2 id=\"levenshtein-distance이-무엇일까\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#levenshtein-distance%EC%9D%B4-%EB%AC%B4%EC%97%87%EC%9D%BC%EA%B9%8C\" aria-label=\"levenshtein distance이 무엇일까 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Levenshtein Distance이 무엇일까?</h2>\n<p>오늘날 <strong>언어학/데이터과학</strong> 같이 폭 넓게 사용되고 있으며 <strong>문장과 DNA 유사도 분석같은 곳에 사용되고 있습니다</strong><br>\n레벤슈타인 알고리즘의 비교 이론은 간단합니다  </p>\n<br/>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">두 비교군의 삽입, 변경, 삭제에 대한 비용을 계산합니다</code>  </p>\n<br/>\n<p>이렇게 두 개의 비교군을 분석하여 연산되는 <span class='red_font'>비용이 높을 수록</span> 서로 다른겁니다  </p>\n<br/>\n<h2 id=\"levenshtein-distance-살펴보기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#levenshtein-distance-%EC%82%B4%ED%8E%B4%EB%B3%B4%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"levenshtein distance 살펴보기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Levenshtein Distance 살펴보기</h2>\n<p>수식으로 확인 하면 다음과 같습니다  </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 690px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 29.47976878612717%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"levenshtein-expression\"\n        title=\"levenshtein-expression\"\n        src=\"/static/f0682c741ee5637d7cd374462e753535/1e043/levenshtein-expression.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f0682c741ee5637d7cd374462e753535/991de/levenshtein-expression.png 173w,\n/static/f0682c741ee5637d7cd374462e753535/e4d6b/levenshtein-expression.png 345w,\n/static/f0682c741ee5637d7cd374462e753535/1e043/levenshtein-expression.png 690w,\n/static/f0682c741ee5637d7cd374462e753535/c0255/levenshtein-expression.png 920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 690px) 100vw, 690px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>  </p>\n<p>굉장히 어려운거 같게 써놨지만 개념을 알고 보면 간단합니다  </p>\n<br/>\n<p>간단한 예제를 통해 비교에 대한 비용 계산을 살펴보겠습니다  </p>\n<ol>\n<li>유사도나 분석 할까요  </li>\n<li>얼마나 분석이 될까요  </li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>이 두개의 문장을 비교해 보겠습니다</strong>  </p>\n<br/>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 690px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 40.46242774566473%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"levenshtein-ex\"\n        title=\"levenshtein-ex\"\n        src=\"/static/c5e00ba2f2c17a666cfd3a93fab291b6/1e043/levenshtein-ex.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c5e00ba2f2c17a666cfd3a93fab291b6/991de/levenshtein-ex.png 173w,\n/static/c5e00ba2f2c17a666cfd3a93fab291b6/e4d6b/levenshtein-ex.png 345w,\n/static/c5e00ba2f2c17a666cfd3a93fab291b6/1e043/levenshtein-ex.png 690w,\n/static/c5e00ba2f2c17a666cfd3a93fab291b6/62de4/levenshtein-ex.png 746w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 690px) 100vw, 690px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<span class='img_caption'>Levenshtein Distance 비교</span>  </p>\n<br/>  \n<p>이렇게 비용을 계산하면 <strong>5만큼 서로 다르다는 계산 결과가 나옵니다</strong>  </p>\n<br/>\n<h2 id=\"levenshtein-distance-알고리즘-방식\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#levenshtein-distance-%EC%95%8C%EA%B3%A0%EB%A6%AC%EC%A6%98-%EB%B0%A9%EC%8B%9D\" aria-label=\"levenshtein distance 알고리즘 방식 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Levenshtein Distance 알고리즘 방식</h2>\n<p>그럼 이런 방법을 어떻게 알고리즘으로 구현할까요?<br>\n방법은 텍스트를 한글자씩 비교해가면서 행렬의 형태로 모든 경우의 수를 계산합니다  </p>\n<br/>\n<p><strong>1. 행과 열로 각각의 비교군을 배치하고 숫자를 순서대로 입력해줍니다</strong>    </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 690px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 82.08092485549133%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"levenshtein-step1\"\n        title=\"levenshtein-step1\"\n        src=\"/static/d7df55923a8b854e789fe08e32655c1e/1e043/levenshtein-step1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d7df55923a8b854e789fe08e32655c1e/991de/levenshtein-step1.png 173w,\n/static/d7df55923a8b854e789fe08e32655c1e/e4d6b/levenshtein-step1.png 345w,\n/static/d7df55923a8b854e789fe08e32655c1e/1e043/levenshtein-step1.png 690w,\n/static/d7df55923a8b854e789fe08e32655c1e/58bb7/levenshtein-step1.png 985w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 690px) 100vw, 690px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<span class='img_caption'>Levenshtein Distance Step 1</span>  </p>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<p><strong>2. 다음으로 한글자식 비교하며 삽입, 변경, 삭제 여부를 결정합니다</strong>  </p>\n<blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li>글자가 서로 동일하면 대각선의 숫자를 가져온다  </li>\n<li>변경이 필요하면 대각선 수의 +1을 한다  </li>\n<li>삽입이 필요한 경우 위의 수에서 +1을 한다  </li>\n<li>삭제가 필요한 경우 왼쪽 수에서 +1을 한다  </li>\n<li>1 ~ 4까지의 숫자 중 가장 낮은 수를 입력한다   </li>\n</ol>\n</blockquote>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 690px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 69.36416184971098%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"levenshtein-step2\"\n        title=\"levenshtein-step2\"\n        src=\"/static/a2a4f4ccc04ffdfaa3fc0034167d3e4b/1e043/levenshtein-process1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a2a4f4ccc04ffdfaa3fc0034167d3e4b/991de/levenshtein-process1.png 173w,\n/static/a2a4f4ccc04ffdfaa3fc0034167d3e4b/e4d6b/levenshtein-process1.png 345w,\n/static/a2a4f4ccc04ffdfaa3fc0034167d3e4b/1e043/levenshtein-process1.png 690w,\n/static/a2a4f4ccc04ffdfaa3fc0034167d3e4b/e3189/levenshtein-process1.png 1035w,\n/static/a2a4f4ccc04ffdfaa3fc0034167d3e4b/6be49/levenshtein-process1.png 1160w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 690px) 100vw, 690px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<span class='img_caption'>Levenshtein Distance Step 2</span>  </p>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<p><strong>3. 이렇게 모든 경우의 수를 반복하면 맨 마지막 수가 비용값이 된다</strong>  </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 690px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 82.08092485549133%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"levenshtein-step3\"\n        title=\"levenshtein-step3\"\n        src=\"/static/a65c303cc273d5808ec53e29443a8608/1e043/levenshtein-process2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a65c303cc273d5808ec53e29443a8608/991de/levenshtein-process2.png 173w,\n/static/a65c303cc273d5808ec53e29443a8608/e4d6b/levenshtein-process2.png 345w,\n/static/a65c303cc273d5808ec53e29443a8608/1e043/levenshtein-process2.png 690w,\n/static/a65c303cc273d5808ec53e29443a8608/91b29/levenshtein-process2.png 983w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 690px) 100vw, 690px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<span class='img_caption'>Levenshtein Distance Step 3</span>  </p>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<h2 id=\"levenshtein-distance-코드-구현하기--code\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#levenshtein-distance-%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C-%EA%B5%AC%ED%98%84%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0--code\" aria-label=\"levenshtein distance 코드 구현하기  code permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Levenshtein Distance 코드 구현하기 👉 <a href=\"https://github.com/renuevo/data-modeling-algorithm/tree/master/levenshtein-distance\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Code</a></h2>\n<p>아래 모든 코드는 예제 출력코드는 github에 등록되어 있습니다  </p>\n<br/>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>연산을 위해 필요한 행의 수는 2개 임으로 List 2개를 생성해 주고 한줄을 초기화해 줍니다    </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token class-name\">List</span><span class=\"token generics\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Integer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> costList <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Lists</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">newArrayList</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token class-name\">List</span><span class=\"token generics\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Integer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> newCostList <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Lists</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">newArrayList</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">//행렬 첫줄 초기화</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;=</span> s1<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">length</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    costList<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">add</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>costList는 이전 행 / newCostList는 연산이 진행되는 행 입니다</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>\n<p>행마다 for문을 돌면서 비용을 계산합니다  </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;=</span> s2<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">length</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    newCostList<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">add</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> i<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> j <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token numb